    <h3>District Information</h3>
    <p>With 5 high schools, the Gilbert Public Schools works hard to provide top quality
education to all of its students. With an array of clubs, sports teams, AP courses and more,
the students are able to get involved in many different activities. Encouraging students to
get involved in the community, they are taught skills necessary to be productive members
of society. Believing in the power of character, teachers try to build a sense of self-pride
that will help students realize their dreams and their potential. With several high schools
recognized with the 'School of Excellence' award, it is easy to see that students learning in
this district are on a launching pad to success. The Gilbert Public Schools has proven to be
the start for a great future.</p>
